<p>US prosecutors unsealed an indictment in Brooklyn charging UK-Cambodian businessman Chen Zhi, chairman of Cambodia’s Prince Holding Group, with wire fraud and money laundering conspiracies tied to a vast cryptocurrency scheme [npr.org#1][scmp.com#1][firstpost.com#1]. Authorities in the US and UK also announced coordinated sanctions against alleged members of a Southeast Asian network that used trafficked workers and forced labour to run global online frauds [aljazeera.com#1][firstpost.com#1]. Investigators say they have seized about $14 billion in bitcoin, and the UK has frozen assets linked to the suspects, including a £100 million London office building [bbc.com#1][scmp.com#1]. Officials say the operation aims to disrupt large-scale online investment scams and choke off funds allegedly laundered into luxury assets [aljazeera.com#1][scmp.com#1]. While the case is ongoing, the cross-border action signals stepped-up efforts to protect consumers and trafficking victims and police crypto-related crime [bbc.com#1][aljazeera.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/TGM8r1e975hlF3w5W5P03Ekj31PCLO6GAM81_Tuvhg-zAJWEb2lKaWKvqHIV_C4KiXg-YpR9GOjx5oP58DVPkxm87bmLjh5N2uU36-06TTEuHb7LSeJiiDunvUA9hS3G7y5_XwLygwvRAhlQKP1Oq55Oba17vIHHhaaFAJEwnZhoIS2-' alt='US and UK authorities move against an alleged Southeast Asian crypto scam network.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Charges filed: Chen Zhi was charged with wire fraud conspiracy and money laundering conspiracy in an indictment unsealed in federal court in Brooklyn [npr.org#1][scmp.com#1].</li><li>Sanctions push: The US and UK imposed sanctions targeting entities and individuals linked to the Prince Group network alleged to run global scams using trafficked workers [aljazeera.com#1].</li><li>Asset actions: Authorities say they seized about $14 billion in bitcoin, while the UK froze assets including a £100 million London office building [bbc.com#1][scmp.com#1].</li><li>Forced labour: Investigators describe the network as exploiting trafficked workers and forced labour to carry out online fraud operations across Asia [aljazeera.com#1][firstpost.com#1].</li><li>Luxury spending: Prosecutors allege scam proceeds funded high-end purchases including yachts, jets, and even a Picasso painting [scmp.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>US prosecutors: They allege Chen Zhi led a vast crypto fraud and money laundering scheme connected to Prince Holding Group. (<a href='https://www.npr.org/2025/10/15/nx-s1-5574948/us-indictment-cambodia-tycoon-alleged-crypto-scam'>NPR</a>)</li><li>UK authorities: They emphasize asset freezes linked to the alleged network, including a £100 million London office building. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c70jw436n0yo'>BBC News</a>)</li><li>US and UK governments: They announced coordinated sanctions targeting entities and individuals linked to the Prince Group network. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/15/us-uk-sanction-huge-southeast-asian-crypto-scam-network'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/us-indicts-uk-cambodian-business-tycoon-over-15-bn-crypto-scam-forced-labour-ws-e-13942137.html'>US indicts UK-Cambodian business tycoon over $15 bn crypto scam, forced labour</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c70jw436n0yo'>Bitcoin worth $14bn seized in US-UK crackdown on alleged scammers</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/15/us-uk-sanction-huge-southeast-asian-crypto-scam-network'>US, UK sanction huge Southeast Asian crypto scam network</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.npr.org/2025/10/15/nx-s1-5574948/us-indictment-cambodia-tycoon-alleged-crypto-scam'>U.S. charges Cambodian tycoon in massive alleged cryptocurrency scam</a> - npr.org</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/3329046/cambodian-tycoon-exposed-mastermind-us14-billion-crypto-fraud-empire'>Cambodian tyc